Title: Hand rails in bronze and brushed stainless steel by Jules Wabbes
Description: Hand rail in cast bronze and brushed stainless steel by Jules Wabbes from the General de Banque Headquarters in Brussels. (1971-1973)Mural attachments in bronze are included in the price. (all handrails with length 228cm and upwards have 3 attachments, below just 2). Different lengths available, pick your size. Can easily be mounted on any solid wall with help of a threaded rod M8 (not included but available in any hardware store)Very good used condition. Beautiful patina. May have a few light scratches. Please note these products are only available in our shop.
